OL,3,CFundraising walk to raise money for
OL,4,Cmother and son injured in house fire
OL,6,FFamily and friends of a mother and son
OL,7,Fwho were severely injured in a house
OL,8,Ffire in Chorley have completed a
OL,9,Ffundraising walk to support them.
OL,11,FKim Leighton and one of her sons,
OL,12,FCole, who's 11, are still in hospital
OL,13,Fwith serious burns after the fire at
OL,14,Ftheir home in Clayton Green last month.
OL,16,FFollowing the fire the local community
OL,17,Frallied around the family, and an
OL,18,Fonline fundraiser has already secured
OL,19,Fmore than #29,000 of their #60,000
OL,20,Ftarget.
