OL,6,FNeighbour Mitch Thomas, who set up the
OL,7,Ffundraiser and helped the family on
OL,8,Fthe night, said: "You could see the
OL,9,Fflames coming out of the windows and
OL,10,Fthe sides. It was already quite severe
OL,11,Fat that point.
OL,13,F"As it developed and got worse, it was
OL,14,Fa bit like a furnace. It was roaring
OL,15,Fangry flames, a lot of smoke and
OL,16,Fthings popping and banging inside. It
OL,17,Fwas aggressive.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
