OL,6,F"Everything's gone unfortunately.
OL,7,FWe're not able to go in to have a look
OL,8,Fbut from what we can see from the
OL,9,Foutside, the whole top floor has gone
OL,10,Fthere's nothing left, it's more like a
OL,11,Fwreckage yard in there."
OL,13,FOn Sunday, family and friends walked
OL,14,Fup to Rivington Pike in Lancashire.
OL,16,FPolice say the cause of the fire is
OL,17,F"subject to a joint investigation
OL,18,Fbetween police and the fire service,
OL,19,Fand enquiries are ongoing".
