OL,6,FIn the immediate aftermath, neighbours
OL,7,Fcame to the support of the family,
OL,8,Fwith people offering first aid and
OL,9,Finviting those who were not injured
OL,10,Finto their house.
OL,12,FCole's brothers, Kian and Bailey,
OL,13,Fhelped Cole out of the house, before
OL,14,Fhe was later taken to hospital.
